I also tried this js to remove the empty inline style="" instead of adding nonce

But it's not trigger, I assume there's also a script added that's why code doesn't work.. Tried to add  no_wrapper=True, in the dnd but no luck

```
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    // Define your nonce value
    const nonceValue = 'MeOG/FwviPIGwQ5ML0hETQ==';

    // Select all elements that have inline styles
    const elementsWithInlineStyle = document.querySelectorAll('[style]');

    // Iterate over each element with inline style
    elementsWithInlineStyle.forEach(element =&gt; {
        // Get the current inline style value
        let inlineStyle = element.getAttribute('style');

        // Check if the element has an inline style attribute
        if (inlineStyle) {
            // Add nonce attribute to the element
            element.setAttribute('nonce', nonceValue);

            // Update the inline style attribute to include the nonce
            element.setAttribute('style', `${inlineStyle}; nonce-${nonceValue}`);
        }
    });
});```
